  <description><![CDATA[<p>The Hotel Eggerwirt is a small and charming hotel in the centre of Kitzbühel.</p>
<h2>A home from home</h2>
<p>The friendly staff have refined the art of traditional Tyrolean hospitality and pride themselves on giving a true home-from-home experience. Offering a perfect combination of modern comforts, tradition and authenticity, the hotel provides a warm welcome to guests looking for a good value option in a prime location.</p>
<h2>Fantastic bed and breakfast hotel</h2>
<p>Fuel up for the day with the generous hot and cold buffet breakfast. A daily packed lunch is available for you to take with you on the mountain. In the evening enjoy the atmosphere over a local beer in the winter garden, and make the most of the bed and breakfast board basis by heading out into the town to try some of the local restaurants.</p>
<h2>Central location</h2>
<p>The hotel is just a short walk from the lively town centre and its array of bars, restaurants and boutiques. It's also within an easy walk are the Hahnenkamm and Hornbahn lifts - gateways to the surrounding mountains, the lifts give access to an abundance of hiking and biking routes, mountain lakes, and alpine restaurants.</p>
<p>Adding comfort to convenience, the hotels spacious bedrooms are tastefully furnished and are the perfect place to rest your head after a day in the mountains.</p>]]></description>
