  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Double Rooms </strong>are around 25-35m² and sleep up to three people with an Austrian Twin bed and a single sofa bed in the seating area. Each is individually styled and comfortable. Rooms are available for sole use for a supplement and there are rooms with a balcony or terrace available for a supplement.</p>
<p><strong>Junior Suites </strong>are around 35m² and sleep two to four people with an Austrian Twin bed and a double sofa bed in the lounge area.</p>
<p><strong>Single Rooms </strong>are around 18m².</p>
<p><strong>All rooms have:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>TV</li>
<li>Safe</li>
<li>Minibar/fridge</li>
<li>Bath or shower</li>
<li>Hairdryer</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>General information</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Check-in: 2pm</li>
<li>Check-out: 11am</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Local fees and taxes</strong></p>
<p>A resort tourist tax of approx. €3.50 per person per night is payable locally. Children under the age of 15yrs are exempt.</p>
<p><strong>Accessibility</strong></p>]]></roomsDescription>
